  <bioghist id="aspace_68cf572d8017515569a295d3563faf67">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Helen Finch Smith was a genealogist.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_1aa8cbe18a96e330a8b567a660cb3831">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Manuscript, typed, mimeographed and printed material derived from family and genealogical research; local, county, court, church and cemetery records; and printed local and family history, primarily in southern and central New York State and nearby Pennsylvania counties. Includes research notes and correspondence concerning Cayuga, Schuyler, Tompkins, Madison, Chenango, Tioga and Chemung Counties, New York.</p>  </scopecontent>
